UNTIL
=========

Conditional clause used in `Do..Loop` statements.

Syntax:

Do Until condition

or

Loop Until condition

Description:
`Until` is used with the `Do...Loop` structure.

Examples:

Dim a As Integer
a = 1
Do
    Print "hello"
a = a + 1
Loop Until a > 10

This will continue to print "hello" on the screen until the condition (a >
10) is met.

Differences from QB:
	None

